import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import ContactsServices from '../Firebase/services' export default function Contact(id) { const [contactData, setContactData] = useState([]) const url = window.location.href const contactId = url.split("?id=")[1] useEffect(()=>{ getContact(); },[]) const getContact = async ()=>{ const data = await ContactsServices.getSingleDoc(contactId); setContactData(data.data()) } return ( <>
ContactView
First Name {contactData.first_name}
Last Name {contactData.last_name}
Email {contactData.email}
Phone Main {contactData.phone_number01}
Phone Secondary {contactData.phone_number02}
Owner ID {contactData.uid}
) }
